Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.08,0:00:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.81,0:00:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢冈崎君 请跟我交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.11,0:00:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 很抱歉 你一定很困扰对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.83,0:00:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然听到这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.82,0:00:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不说出来我会很难受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.48,0:00:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.81,0:00:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.52,0:00:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们也才刚认识不久吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.26,0:00:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然经常有跟杏三个人一起吃吃饭什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也 也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是说我讨厌你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.75,0:00:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是说从没当作恋爱对象看待过呢 还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.87,0:00:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 这种说法很失礼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.76,0:01:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样也不介意的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.70,0:01:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要试着交往看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.67,0:01:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们接下来会逐渐了解对方的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我觉得接下来的时间不是作为朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.45,0:01:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是作为男女朋友来度过的话可能也不坏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.09,0:01:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.25,0:01:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在起你就是我的女朋友了 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.37,0:01:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 眼泪 控制不住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.27,0:01:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是做梦一样 好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的志愿是护士学校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 那是我从小的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对将来的事完全没考虑过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.23,0:03:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我认为不用着急
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.76,0:03:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行 如果整天游手好闲的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定会被你讨厌了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.29,0:03:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事绝不可能发生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论发生什么事 我都不会讨厌冈崎君的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.50,0:03:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.98,0:03:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为还从没有人对我说过这样的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.95,0:03:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点感动了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.53,0:03:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 杏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.91,0:04:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大好的星期天你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好陪在椋身边怎么行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 别瞎操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.61,0:04:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从二年级开始就一直喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 你觉得你们能好好发展下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该能行吧 她又认真又温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.37,0:04:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸动不动就红 所以稍微让人有点担心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错 不过她的这种地方也很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:04:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:05:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 你可真是什么事都想着妹妹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.62,0:05:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不尽是如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.34,0:05:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟椋接过吻了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.97,0:05:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？ 才 才没做过那种事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么行 你要更主动一些才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说… 我可是第一次跟女生交往啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.83,0:05:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么要练习一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.24,0:05:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.24,0:05:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就把我当成椋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是双胞胎 感觉上也很像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.81,0:05:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.76,0:05:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是练习 真亲了可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你刚才当真了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.62,0:06:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.86,0:06:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你个及格分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是在那公园里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈崎不就是那个不良少年吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.96,0:06:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是那两人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.32,0:06:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们原来是同班 而且现在关系似乎也很不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.01,0:06:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.76,0:06:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.42,0:06:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算再怎样也不能在那种地方 对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.11,0:06:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道就没一点羞耻感吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好啊 冈崎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么连你也这样了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.92,0:06:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？ 我跟杏？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:56.70,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在走廊里跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:07:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经传遍整个学校了 说你昨天跟杏接了吻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 不 那个该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那么一回事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别装傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.83,0:07:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过呢 我也觉得你最近不太正常
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.81,0:07:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去很开心的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不说了我没做过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说跟我交往的是她妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？ 你跟藤林椋？ 真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这么意外吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.28,0:07:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们俩性格完全不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是杏的话我倒还能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别随便下结论
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这传闻藤林估计也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正只要在学校就算不想听也会传进耳朵里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 在这儿在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微陪我一下 不会浪费你太多时间的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.47,0:07:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛… 什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可什么也没做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏 我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.14,0:08:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊 说实话确实是难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.89,0:08:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊 我所说的话就那么奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 一直以来不是从来都没有过这种感觉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是那个吧 因为过于接近而无法察觉的心意？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢 差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.89,0:08:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 让你见识一下显而易见的证据吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.26,0:08:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很奇怪啊 你真的喜欢我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.09,0:08:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说错了的话我向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏 你应该是喜欢冈崎的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:08:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.57,0:09:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.68,0:09:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 想消除自己跟你的流言才想跟我交往啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.83,0:09:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流言什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.42,0:09:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是流言的话 何必做到这种地步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.99,0:09:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊 阳平说过的话你可别当真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着你跟椋关系那么好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.48,0:09:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想着「我也交个男朋友多好」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就想干脆就找阳平好了 于是就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.79,0:09:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道因为这么简单的理由就去找男人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:09:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是多管什么闲事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要想着椋的事就行了 知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让女朋友担心的男人最差劲了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.78,0:10:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.32,0:10:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一共八百日元
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想试着叫叫你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不愿意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.42,0:10:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 像杏还不是直呼我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.59,0:10:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢 都已经是这种关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:11:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不介意的话也叫我椋好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.32,0:11:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋 朋也君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.29,0:11:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天…见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.05,0:11:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去春原那儿好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牡丹？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.69,0:11:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可是星期天 没人会来的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牡丹 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.24,0:11:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:11:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.55,0:12:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 你不是跟椋去约会了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.00,0:12:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都完全湿透了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.80,0:12:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.10,0:12:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要想着椋的事就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.98,0:12:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟你是椋的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在跟这些没关系吧 你会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要管我 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.00,0:12:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就别再管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.91,0:12:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.47,0:12:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.12,0:13:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别对我这么温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.65,0:13:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是个笨蛋 你对我温柔的话我会误会的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好害怕 害怕去告白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.42,0:13:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果向你告白 被拒绝了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.71,0:13:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许就连朋友也做不成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.00,0:13:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果和你交往了 又会让椋伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.45,0:13:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样 还不如放弃了好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为只有这样才不会有人受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 我现在心里只有后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.77,0:13:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是笨呢 明明是自己已经决定了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.47,0:13:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.34,0:13:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.43,0:14:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是藤林杏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.10,0:14:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是椋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也的确是个难题呢 在双胞胎之间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你 会怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.43,0:14:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我站在你的立场上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还有什么好说的 自然是两人都要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.09,0:14:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以把你揍到爬不起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.44,0:14:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过说真的 确实是很难办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:14:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样干脆…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.36,0:15:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.97,0:15:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想跟双方都保持距离的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就真是个极品废柴了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.31,0:15:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊 想让自己一直保持清白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.65,0:15:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然事已至此 无论怎样你都会伤害其中一方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你越晚给出答案 伤害就会越深
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你们三人中的任何人都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便 我能再说一句吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的烦恼太奢侈了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.56,0:15:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.62,0:15:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 觅食了觅食了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.66,0:16:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.54,0:16:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要跟我说的是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我们两个人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是漫画的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.30,0:16:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人独处在放学后的教室里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.85,0:16:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会接吻什么的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤林
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要用姓称呼我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…一直想着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想输给姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐一直在注视着谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.47,0:16:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明知道 却仍然去找姐姐商量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说我想跟朋也君搞好关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:17:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐虽然很吃惊 但还是马上笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.51,0:17:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说包在她身上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.61,0:17:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明知道她会那么说 也明白自己很卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.50,0:17:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.44,0:17:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此我也想待在朋也君身边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.55,0:17:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不能替代姐姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会变得像姐姐一样主动的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会留长头发 也会学习做料理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会成为朋也君心仪的女生的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.56,0:17:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望你做那些事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想待在朋也君身边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.83,0:17:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么下一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤林…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.93,0:18:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 请假了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.19,0:18:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 铃木
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.76,0:18:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你交往的那些日子我真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.04,0:19:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次明白被人需要是多么开心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.62,0:19:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想着能跟你很好地相处下去 就这样处下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是果然不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.23,0:19:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了一件最差劲的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.24,0:19:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有了你 却还想着别人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.66,0:19:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我注意到这事后 也没有告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我利用了你的温柔 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.49,0:19:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.86,0:19:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.43,0:19:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.20,0:19:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你的头发…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.62,0:19:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被骂了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.66,0:20:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椋跟我说「不要逃避」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想着一直保持这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.75,0:20:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜伤害椋也要选择你 这样卑鄙的事我不想做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.95,0:20:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她却说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「这是不可能的」 「已经太晚了」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「如果真的喜欢朋也 那就不能再逃避了」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.07,0:20:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我们不管怎样 总是会有人受到伤害的」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.38,0:20:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「毕竟我们喜欢上了同一个人」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她现在一定在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们真的是…太晚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.57,0:20:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是觉察 蒙混 还是面对都太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.53,0:20:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.01,0:20:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这将是最后一次伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是那孩子 我 还是朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.71,0:21:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你 朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.11,0:21:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直 一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.03,0:21:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都喜欢着你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.82,0:21:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.95,0:21:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.16,0:21:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果接受你的道歉 原谅了你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.07,0:21:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让我感觉这全都是假的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.11,0:21:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把那段时光当作珍贵的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.22,0:21:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是开心的事 悲伤的事 所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:21:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 请你不要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.91,0:22:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.98,0:22:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天啊 要去哪儿来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.52,0:22:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约好了要去玩的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.70,0:22:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉 那个取消了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.77,0:22:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为难得椋说想去买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.43,0:22:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.23,0:22:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那没办法了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.75,0:22:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.34,0:22:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近可真是热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.45,0:22:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.68,0:22:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 我真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.05,0:22:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会不会觉得还是跟椋在一起更舒服？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.42,0:22:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊 我可要生气了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.60,0:22:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.04,0:22:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样我才能稍微安心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.28,0:22:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是有点扭曲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:23:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就更直截了当一点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.87,0:23:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.38,0:23:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.88,0:23:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.30,0:23:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到夏天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.45,0:23:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯


